longBusinessSummary: Haidilao International Holding Ltd., an investment holding company, engages in the restaurant chain operation and delivery businesses. It operates a Haidilao branded Chinese cuisine restaurant that focuses on hot pot cuisine. The company is also involved in the sale of condiment products and food ingredients; logistics and wholesale trade activities; management consultation; financial management; and food research and development, and trading businesses. As of December 31, 2020, it owned and operated 1,298 restaurants, including 1,205 restaurants in Mainland China, as well as 93 restaurants in Hong Kong, Macao, Taiwan, Singapore, Vietnam, Malaysia, Indonesia, South Korea, Japan, the United Kingdom, the United States, Canada, and Australia. Haidilao International Holding Ltd. was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.
address2: 7th Floor No. 398 Yard, Zhongdong Road Dongxiaokou Town, Changping District
